    Reads a GraphML file possibly with attributes on nodes and edges (such as weights).
    1. Use one of the factory methods create(java.io.Reader), createFromClasspathResource(String), or createFromFile(java.io.File) to create an importer.
    2. Use edgeAttributeHandler(AttributeHandler) and/or nodeAttributeHandler(AttributeHandler) to specify how to handle attributes.
    3. Use the generateGraph(org.jgrapht.Graph, org.jgrapht.VertexFactory, java.util.Map) as with any GraphGenerator to map the GraphML file onto a Graph object
